<p>罗在和之国会颠覆想象，手术果实将重创凯多。</p>
<p>第一、罗杰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200923/695929b472dc4946be91c60dc5bdc491.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
